Resource Profile: CH EPREG Organization: Treating Healthcare Provider

Official URL: http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-epreg/StructureDefinition/ch-epreg-organization-thcp Version: 1.0.0-ballot
Active as of 2025-05-22 Computable Name: ChEpregOrganizationTHCP

Copyright/Legal: CC0-1.0

This profile constrains the Organization resource to represent the treating healthcare provider.

Usage:

  • Refer to this Resource Profile: CH EPREG PractitionerRole: Treating Healthcare Provider
